abstract: A Michigan man recently identified as the newborn boy snatched from his mother in 1964 by someone posing as a maternity-ward nurse was found through commercial ancestry websites after the man or a child of his submitted DNA to the sites to learn more about their family tree, a genetic genealogist who played a role in the discovery told The Associated Press Friday.
snippet: A Michigan man recently identified as the newborn boy snatched from his mother in 1964 by someone posing as a maternity-ward nurse was found through commercial ancestry websites after the man or a child of his submitted DNA to the sites to learn m...
lead_paragraph: CHICAGO — A Michigan man recently identified as the newborn boy snatched from his mother in 1964 by someone posing as a maternity-ward nurse was found through commercial ancestry websites after the man or a child of his submitted DNA to the sites to learn more about their family tree, a genetic genealogist who played a role in the discovery told The Associated Press Friday.
headline_main: Boy Kidnapped in 1964 Found Through Ancestry Sites
headline_print_headline: Boy Kidnapped in 1964 Found Through Ancestry Sites

abstract: President Donald Trump escaped the chill of Washington and his impeachment on Friday to celebrate Christmas and New Year's in sunny Florida with family and friends.
snippet: President Donald Trump escaped the chill of Washington and his impeachment on Friday to celebrate Christmas and New Year's in sunny Florida with family and friends.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Donald Trump escaped the chill of Washington and his impeachment on Friday to celebrate Christmas and New Year's in sunny Florida with family and friends.
headline_main: Trump Escapes Chill of Washington for Florida Holiday
headline_print_headline: Trump Escapes Chill of Washington for Florida Holiday

abstract: Be a splendid companion this holiday season and New Year.
snippet: Be a splendid companion this holiday season and New Year.
lead_paragraph: If you’re going to be a guest at someone else’s holiday party this year, a little awareness and volunteering on your part can help the host relax.

abstract: Buffalo got its first bowl win, and Jaret Patterson put an exclamation point on his record-setting season.
snippet: Buffalo got its first bowl win, and Jaret Patterson put an exclamation point on his record-setting season.
lead_paragraph: NASSAU, Bahamas — Buffalo got its first bowl win, and Jaret Patterson put an exclamation point on his record-setting season.
headline_main: Buffalo Tops Charlotte 31-9 in Bahamas Bowl
headline_print_headline: Buffalo Tops Charlotte 31-9 in Bahamas Bowl

abstract: Ward Just, a highly regarded political and war correspondent for The Washington Post who later drew upon his experiences for such acclaimed novel as “An Unfinished Season” and "Echo House," has died. He was 84.
snippet: Ward Just, a highly regarded political and war correspondent for The Washington Post who later drew upon his experiences for such acclaimed novel as “An Unfinished Season” and "Echo House," has died. He was 84.
lead_paragraph: NEW YORK — Ward Just, a highly regarded political and war correspondent for The Washington Post who later drew upon his experiences for such acclaimed novel as “An Unfinished Season” and "Echo House," has died. He was 84.
headline_main: Acclaimed Author and Journalist Ward Just Dead at 84
headline_print_headline: Acclaimed Author and Journalist Ward Just Dead at 84

abstract: West Point and Naval Academy investigations found that cadets and midshipmen were playing “the circle game” during an ESPN broadcast of the Army-Navy game on Saturday.
snippet: West Point and Naval Academy investigations found that cadets and midshipmen were playing “the circle game” during an ESPN broadcast of the Army-Navy game on Saturday.
lead_paragraph: Military officials said on Friday that their investigations had found that Army cadets and Navy midshipmen who flashed hand symbols during a nationally televised football pregame show last week were playing a juvenile game known as “the circle game,” and not making hand gestures associated with white nationalists and other hate groups.

abstract: Diagnostic tests for Alzheimer’s disease are already here. But the results may raise as many questions as they answer.
snippet: Diagnostic tests for Alzheimer’s disease are already here. But the results may raise as many questions as they answer.
lead_paragraph: Not long ago, the only way to know if someone had Alzheimer’s disease was to examine the brain in an autopsy.

abstract: The average salary in the major leagues has dropped in consecutive years for the first time since the players' association started keeping records more than a half-century ago.
snippet: The average salary in the major leagues has dropped in consecutive years for the first time since the players' association started keeping records more than a half-century ago.
lead_paragraph: NEW YORK — The average salary in the major leagues has dropped in consecutive years for the first time since the players' association started keeping records more than a half-century ago.
headline_main: Average MLB Salary Drops for 2nd Straight Year
headline_print_headline: Average MLB Salary Drops for 2nd Straight Year

abstract: Oregon is renowned for its craft beer and increasingly for its high-grade marijuana, but the state is keeping the two apart — for now.
